AzurVeda VedaLib3DEngine
This library extends VedaLib 's BaseObject to provide classes for AzurVeda contexts.
It is a simple 3D object management Library that uses a VirtualMachine,
 for experimental purposes. It also features "lwo2reader" an independant
 lightwave object file format reader, written in c, with the same authors and license.
Please read the documentation in the headers.
author: victorien ferry & www.m4nkind.com
